{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_013iDtTrLsk5Wu6meUcmEQbs","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Here are the relevant sections from the migration file:\n\n## 1. `challenges` table schema (lines 65-81)\n\n```sql\nCREATE TABLE challenges (\n  id              BIGINT GENERATED ALWAYS AS IDENTITY PRIMARY KEY,\n  campaign_id     BIGINT NOT NULL REFERENCES campaigns(id),\n  title           TEXT NOT NULL,\n  description     TEXT,\n  action          TEXT NOT NULL,\n  scope           TEXT NOT NULL DEFAULT 'any' CHECK (scope IN ('any', 'coinflip', 'lord', 'closecall')),\n  condition       TEXT NOT NULL DEFAULT 'count',\n  threshold       INT NOT NULL,\n  reward_type     TEXT NOT NULL CHECK (reward_type IN ('points', 'crate')),\n  reward_amount   INT,\n  prerequisite_id BIGINT REFERENCES challenges(id),\n  eligible_if     JSONB NOT NULL DEFAULT '{}',\n  sort_order      INT NOT NULL DEFAULT 0,\n  is_active       BOOLEAN NOT NULL DEFAULT true,\n  created_at      TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL DEFAULT now()\n);\n```\n\n## 2. `challenge_assignments` table schema (lines 84-96)\n\n```sql\nCREATE TABLE challenge_assignments (\n  id              BIGINT GENERATED ALWAYS AS IDENTITY PRIMARY KEY,\n  user_id         TEXT NOT NULL,\n  challenge_id    BIGINT NOT NULL REFERENCES challenges(id),\n  period_key      TEXT NOT NULL,\n  status          TEXT NOT NULL DEFAULT 'active' CHECK (status IN ('active', 'completed', 'expired')),\n  progress        INT NOT NULL DEFAULT 0,\n  target          INT NOT NULL,\n  assigned_at     TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL DEFAULT now(),\n  expires_at      TIMESTAMPTZ,\n  completed_at    TIMESTAMPTZ,\n  UNIQUE (user_id, challenge_id, period_key)\n);\n```\n\n## 3. `campaigns` table schema (lines 53-62)\n\n```sql\nCREATE TABLE campaigns (\n  id              BIGINT GENERATED ALWAYS AS IDENTITY PRIMARY KEY,\n  name            TEXT NOT NULL UNIQUE,\n  campaign_type   TEXT NOT NULL CHECK (campaign_type IN ('daily', 'weekly', 'onboarding', 'dogpile')),\n  starts_at       TIMESTAMPTZ,\n  ends_at         TIMESTAMPTZ,\n  is_active       BOOLEAN NOT NULL DEFAULT true,\n  config          JSONB NOT NULL DEFAULT '{}',\n  created_at      TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL DEFAULT now()\n);\n```\n\n## 4. Seed data for onboarding challenges (lines 221-234)\n\n**Step 1: Initial challenge (no prerequisite)**\n```sql\nINSERT INTO challenges (campaign_id, title, description, action, scope, condition, threshold, reward_type, reward_amount, prerequisite_id, sort_order) VALUES\n  ((SELECT id FROM campaigns WHERE name = 'Onboarding'), 'Play Your First Game', 'Complete any game to get started', 'game_completed', 'any', 'count', 1, 'points', 1000, NULL, 1);\n```\n\n**Step 2: Challenge with step 1 as prerequisite**\n```sql\nINSERT INTO challenges (campaign_id, title, description, action, scope, condition, threshold, reward_type, reward_amount, prerequisite_id, sort_order) VALUES\n  ((SELECT id FROM campaigns WHERE name = 'Onboarding'), 'Win a Game', 'Win any game', 'game_won', 'any', 'count', 1, 'points', 1500,\n   (SELECT id FROM challenges WHERE campaign_id = (SELECT id FROM campaigns WHERE name = 'Onboarding') AND sort_order = 1), 2);\n```\n\n**Step 3: Challenge with step 2 as prerequisite**\n```sql\nINSERT INTO challenges (campaign_id, title, description, action, scope, condition, threshold, reward_type, reward_amount, prerequisite_id, sort_order) VALUES\n  ((SELECT id FROM campaigns WHERE name = 'Onboarding'), 'Try All 3 Game Types', 'Play coinflip, jackpot, and close call', 'game_completed', 'any', 'unique_game_types', 3, 'points', 2500,\n   (SELECT id FROM challenges WHERE campaign_id = (SELECT id FROM campaigns WHERE name = 'Onboarding') AND sort_order = 2), 3);\n```\n\n**Key notes:**\n- **`prerequisite_id`** is `BIGINT REFERENCES challenges(id)` — allows self-referential dependencies\n- **`period_key`** (in `challenge_assignments`) is `TEXT NOT NULL` — used to group assignments by time period\n- **`expires_at`** (in `challenge_assignments`) is `TIMESTAMPTZ` nullable — challenges without a deadline have NULL\n- The onboarding challenges form a 3-step chain where each later step depends on completing the previous one"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"a8262916-ffcb-4b28-90e1-2b18f6c84ba5","uuid":"96b4cbe2-baeb-4a66-8e50-85a6abe2a450","timestamp":"2026-04-03T20:34:07.707Z","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"Read the file `/workspaces/rng-utopia/backend/services/backend/migrations/011_challenge_engine.sql` and report the schema for:\n1. The `challenges` table (all columns, especially `prerequisite_id`)\n2. The `challenge_assignments` table (all columns, especially `period_key`, `expires_at`)\n3. The `campaigns` table\n4. Any seed data for onboarding challenges (INSERT statements)\n\nReport relevant sections verbatim.","agentId":"a83e15acb00950a2f","agentType":"Explore","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Here are the relevant sections from the migration file:\n\n## 1. `challenges` table schema (lines 65-81)\n\n```sql\nCREATE TABLE challenges (\n  id              BIGINT GENERATED ALWAYS AS IDENTITY PRIMARY KEY,\n  campaign_id     BIGINT NOT NULL REFERENCES campaigns(id),\n  title           TEXT NOT NULL,\n  description     TEXT,\n  action          TEXT NOT NULL,\n  scope           TEXT NOT NULL DEFAULT 'any' CHECK (scope IN ('any', 'coinflip', 'lord', 'closecall')),\n  condition       TEXT NOT NULL DEFAULT 'count',\n  threshold       INT NOT NULL,\n  reward_type     TEXT NOT NULL CHECK (reward_type IN ('points', 'crate')),\n  reward_amount   INT,\n  prerequisite_id BIGINT REFERENCES challenges(id),\n  eligible_if     JSONB NOT NULL DEFAULT '{}',\n  sort_order      INT NOT NULL DEFAULT 0,\n  is_active       BOOLEAN NOT NULL DEFAULT true,\n  created_at      TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL DEFAULT now()\n);\n```\n\n## 2. `challenge_assignments` table schema (lines 84-96)\n\n```sql\nCREATE TABLE challenge_assignments (\n  id              BIGINT GENERATED ALWAYS AS IDENTITY P